title: Add canonical MCP identities pagination list_changed and metadata limits
updated_at: "2026-07-12T22:30:03Z"
---
Acceptance: MCP tools use collision-safe server plus remote-name identity and an explicit server/tool revision. tools/list pagination is drained and list_changed immediately quarantines only the affected server/revision for new turns before relisting. Failed, malformed, or timed-out relists leave that server unavailable pending successful retry or explicit repair; removed tools never remain discoverable. Names, descriptions, annotations, and schemas have documented size, depth, and control-character validation, and hostile or colliding definitions fail closed. Tests cover removal, malformed pages, timeout, duplicate notifications, and a concurrent invocation racing quarantine. Canonical contract: docs/plans/2026-07-12-github-item-room-routing.md.